FREE STANDARD SHIPPING on orders of $25 or more
How to get FREE Standard Shipping:
  1. Ship to an address within the United States (including U.S. territories)
  2. Place your online order of $25 or more* - after promotions and before tax are applied
  3. Use "Standard" shipping option at checkout

Orders will be shipped within 48 hours of placement*, pending verification of billing information and shipping method selected. International orders and orders containing gift cards or out-of-stock items will be processed as quickly as possible.

 

*Excludes all orders placed on major US holidays (Memorial Day, Independence Day, Labor Day, Thanksgiving Day, Christmas Day and New Year's Day).

 

Orders for states outside of the continental U.S. (including those of $25 or more) may be subject to a delivery surcharge. This will be noted in the order summary based on your shipping address at checkout.

 

Why Pick Up In-Store?

Skip the shippingand the line. Buy online and well have your order bagged and ready for you. Easy. Learn more here.
